## Proposed Changes
---
### Backend API
#### [MODIFY] backend/src/controllers/auth.controller.ts
- **Functionality**: Append a [logout](file:///c:/Users/USER/Documents/WELILE/RENTFLOWINSIGHT/frontend/src/contexts/AuthContext.tsx#52-56) controller explicitly designed to revoke sessions and register audit trails.
- **Auditing**: Mandate execution of [logSecurityEvent({ event: 'LOGOUT_SUCCESS', user_id: req.user.id })](file:///c:/Users/USER/Documents/WELILE/RENTFLOWINSIGHT/backend/src/utils/logger.ts#25-57) to satisfy the "Logging & Auditing (CRITICAL)" section.
